  "text": "Considering that facial attributes contain more detailed characteristics than the full face, we believe that facial attributes would bring new opportunities for biometric identification in real-world applications. [CITATION_1] have attempted the active authentication of mobile devices by facial attributes. A set of binary attribute classifiers are trained to estimate whether attributes are present in images of the current user in a mobile device. Consequently, the authentication can be implemented by comparing the recognized attributes with the originally enrolled attributes.",
